#|
A Template (T) is one of:
  - pvar
  - const (including () and non-pvar identifiers)
  - (metafunction . T)
  - (H . T)
  - (H ... . T), (H ... ... . T), etc
  - (?? T T)
  - #(T*)
  - #s(prefab-struct-key T*)
  * (unquote expr)

A HeadTemplate (H) is one of:
  - T
  - (?? H)
  - (?? H H)
  - (?@ . T)
  * (unquote-splicing expr)
|#

